high_descs: Turn around and head to the dining table on the left.
Pick up the knife from the dining table.
Head right to face the lettuce on the dining table.
Cut the lettuce with the knife on the dining table.

Put the knife on the dining table.

Cool the slice of lettuce in the fridge and take it out.

Put the slice of lettuce in the microwave.

Pick up knife from the table.
Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the table.
Slice lettuce into pieces.
Move little bit back on the table
place knife on the dining table
Move back from the dining table

Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the fridge.
keep lettuce inside the fridge and cool it

Take a knife from the table
Little bit move towards right side of the dining table
Cut the lettuce which is kept on the table
Hold the knife in hand and stand in front of the dining table
Put the knife on the dining table
Head towards the cut lettuce
Take a lettuce piece from the cut lettuce

Open the fridge and put the lettuce piece inside it and close the door. After few seconds open the door and take the lettuce piece out and close the door again
